{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>你是否經常苦惱於會議記錄錯漏百出，或是上課時手寫筆記跟不上教授語速？《AI Lecture Note Taker》就是你一直在尋找的智能解決方案，今天限時免費中，它專為需要高效記錄與整理語音內容的學生、專業人士及任何學習者而設計，讓你在任何場合都能輕鬆捕捉每一分細節，有效提升學習和工作效率。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-99.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>全面提升學習與工作效率</h2>\n    <p>這款應用搭載先進 AI 語音轉文字技術，支援多語言且可離線運作，確保會議與講座內容被精準捕捉。其 AI 摘要功能可快速提煉重點，AI 聊天助手則能回答筆記疑問，並利用 AI 學習工具自動生成抽認卡與測驗，大幅提升學習與工作效率。此外，應用提供智能編輯功能，如點擊文字跳轉音訊及關鍵字搜尋，讓筆記整理更加便捷。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-138-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-139-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-140-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-141-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-142-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-143-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：AI Lecture Note Taker</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Productivity</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T17:16:20.917238+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":373,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}